jQuery 1.4.x or later is required.

Steps:
1 - Load reqman.js
2 - Wrap every AJAX request with the add() function, like this: RQ.add("my_unique_id",$.post(....))
3 - Then, if you wanna kill all pending requests, just execute RQ.killAll()
4 - Or kill a single request with RQ.kill("my_unique_id")

That's all folks!

